        <body>

            <pb n="1"/>

            <p>&#40;The &#40;bad&#41; Hebrew of this letter is as follows&#41;&#58;&#8211;</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">And now my friend and beloved&#44;<lb/> very secretly I shall reveal to you that<lb/>
                many of my friends advise me to go to<lb/>
                <placeName>San Francisco</placeName>. Since for many years past<lb/> you have given
                me clear proof that you<lb/> love me as a brother. Write to me <del>from
                the</del><lb/> very seriously about this matter. Many<lb/> people tell me that it
                will be a great<lb/> thing for a man like me&#44; and that&#44;
                un&#8211;<lb/>doubtedly&#44; I will be able to support my<lb/> household. I hope you
                will reply quickly&#44;<lb/> for if I write to those people about this<lb/>
                matter&#44; I shall reveal my plan to the<lb/> directors of the school&#44;
                since&#44; in any<lb/> event&#44; I am compelled to tell<lb/> them about it. My
                friend&#44; the Chazan&#44;<lb/> who works with me&#44; keeps on telling<lb/> me to
                write&#44; and that&#44; undoubtedly&#44; they<lb/> will receive me with open arms.
                I await<lb/> your reply and shall act according<lb/> to your advice. Your
                everlasting friend&#44;<lb/>
                <persName role="author">Simon&#8211;Noht</persName></p>

            <p>P.S. Undoubtedly I'll be able to transact business three<lb/> for there is
                merchandise in plenty&#44; especially of the Ashke&#8211;<lb/>nazic Minhag&#59; such
                as Hebrew books&#44; prayer shawls of<lb/> all kinds.</p>


        </body>
    </text>
